+	 * Current estimate of the device peak rate, measured in
+	 * [(sectors/usec) / 2^BFQ_RATE_SHIFT]. The left-shift by
+	 * BFQ_RATE_SHIFT is performed to increase precision in
+	 * fixed-point calculations.
